def dispatch_request(self, request): \l return Response('Hello World!')
def wsgi_app(self, environ, start_response):\l request = Request(environ)\l response = self.dispatch_request(request)\l return response(environ, start_response)
def __call__(self, environ, start_response): \l return self.wsgi_app(environ, start_response)
